<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-STATE-POLITICS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
AS STATE LAWMAKERS' POWER INCREASES, SO DOES GRIDLOCK 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
