<SLUG> BC-R-IS-WEEK-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
UNDATED: RALPH BLUMENTHAL 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Repeating for all needing.)
<TEXT>
<P>
   Party Nixed
</P>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ It was to be one of those lavish celebrations that
