<HEADLINE>
YOU'RE NOT OLDER. PRODUCTS ARE BETTER. 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(DW) 
 By WILLIAM L. HAMILTON   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
