<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-28 12:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5133 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-R-SCOTUS-REVIEW-ART-4     06-28 0956
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-SCOTUS-REVIEW-ART-4THTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
 
WASHINGTON: reasonable accommodations.  
<TEXT>
