<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-28 13:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1989 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOSPITAL-PINCH-2TAKES     06-28 1617
