<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-28 15:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2074 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OLIPHANT-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      06-28 0752
