<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-28 15:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2081 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCI-TENNIS-BOS &LR;      06-28 0724
