<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-28 15:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2085 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOSPITAL-PINCH-2TAKES     06-28 1621
