<P>
   KOSOVO-SERBS _ PRISTINA, Yugoslavia _ On the Serbs' most sacred
holiday commorating a defeat by the Ottomans in 1389, Serb Orthodox
Church leaders say their people need protection in Kosovo again.
They also repeated heir condemnation opf Yugoslav President
Slobodan Milosevic. But many Serbs still do not Acknowledge the
atrocities commited in their name and ethnic Albanians wonder where
the church was when they needed help. (Kaplow, Cox News Service).
25.
