<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    South's leaders urge cooperation in tech jobs hunt
 &HT;    (EDS: Moving to (f) Financial and (a) General news categories.)
 &HT;    By Chris Burritt
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Leaders who are charting the South's future urged
